                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="addteam" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            Click the school link in the upper right menu (you must have a school set up to add a team)
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Click the Add Team button in the Team section
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
